{
  "name": "working-discipline",
  "version": "1.6.0",
  "description": "AI 工作纪律注入 + 拦截 - 上下文管理（含 macOS 中文路径 NFC/NFD 防漏检）/ 子代理协作（在飞≤16 动态上限·嵌套≤2 软约束）/ 表达约束（含求真·简体中文·列表编号）/ 思维模式（含落地写 md 前的受众分辨）/ Agent 工具派发 / 外部写操作授权（dws 钉钉 CLI 默认只读，写操作须逐批许可）。UserPromptSubmit 覆盖主会话每轮，SubagentStart 覆盖子代理；PreToolUse 硬拦截污染 cwd 的独立 cd 命令（block-cd）与缺 --headed 的 agent-browser 启动类命令（agent-browser-headed，禁止 AI 起 headless Chrome for Testing 让用户看不到操作过程）；PostToolUse 硬拦截超 1000 行的单一源码文件（max-source-lines）与超 200 行的 CLAUDE.md（claude-md-max-lines，命中提示拆到 .claude/rules/ 而非压缩正文）",
  "author": {
    "name": "zhangq"
  },
  "hooks": {
    "PreToolUse": [
      {
        "matcher": "Bash",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "node ${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT}/hooks/guards/block-cd.js"
          },
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "node ${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT}/hooks/guards/agent-browser-headed.js"
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "PostToolUse": [
      {
        "matcher": "Write|Edit",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "node ${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT}/hooks/guards/max-source-lines.js"
          },
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "node ${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT}/hooks/guards/claude-md-max-lines.js"
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "UserPromptSubmit": [
      {
        "matcher": "*",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "node ${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT}/hooks/working-discipline.js"
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "SubagentStart": [
      {
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "node ${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT}/hooks/working-discipline.js"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
